description: KANNA Weed Dispensary Oakland is your premier destination for top-quality cannabis products and exceptional customer service. Located in the heart of Oakland, California, our dispensary offers a wide selection of meticulously curated cannabis strains, concentrates, edibles, and more. We take pride in sourcing our cannabis products from trusted and reputable local growers and suppliers. From potent indica strains to uplifting sativas and everything in between, we have something for every taste and preference. Let us be your trusted weed dispensary and cannabis delivery partner for wellness, relaxation, and enjoyment. Visit our cannabis store at MacArthur Blvd or order online and enjoy our reliable weed delivery services.

Visit us Sunday to enjoy our Caribbean Breakfast Brunch

- Join us this Sunday 10am-1:30pm for a Special Trip to the islands! Caribbean Breakfast Brunch featuring Bottomless Tropical Mimosas, Carib Beer, Superfood Waffles, Coconut Bake, Fry Bake, Saltfish, Omelettes, Vegan Tofu Scramble, Bacon, Sausage, Eggplant Choka, Passionfruit Juice, Mushroom Coffee Latte, and so much more....

Sunday is Caribbean Feast Day

- Enjoy our Caribbean Feast Prix-Fixe Four Course Meal for Two 
- Featuring: Your choice of two of our bestselling Caribbean Appetizers, Superfood Juices, Artisan Desserts and Dinner Entrees served with sunshine salad, two deep-fried plantains, Chef Ann's signature spicy pineapple dressing, and spicy island pineapple chow.
- Two Appetizers Two Dinner Entrees Two Drinks Two Desserts
- Available Standard, Vegan, or Gluten-Free
- Some our bestsellers options include but not limited to our award winning Spicy Jerk Chicken Dinner, mild Caribbean Braised Oxtails Dinner, mild Curry Chicken Roti, Vegan Curry Chicken with Pelau peas and rice, spicy Jerk Vegan Fish w/ sauteed veggies and rice, Whole Fried Escovitch Red Snapper Fish w spicy sauteed veggies and rice, Accra Saltfish Fritters, Jamaican Beef or Veggie patties, Trini Doubles, Coconut Roll Pastries and more!", "timestamp": 1743353060, "link": "https://search.google.com/local/posts?q=Cocobreeze+Caribbean+Restaurant+and+Bakery&ludocid=14955786656916974725&lpsid=CIHM0ogKEICAgMCI1JvC5wE&source=sh/x/localposts&lsig=AB86z5XX7AmrGi349Wf1W6gpY3QD", "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc/AF1QipM8b_k0p9_LydKlrcXxBOzFOJ9r29wQ9N63XEpM=h400-no"}, {"body": "SATURDAY IS OXTAILS DAY!

Brown Stew Red Snapper Fish w/ Coo-Coo and Callaloo. Red Snapper marinated with Chef Ann's fresh herb seasoning and stewed down in a savory brown sauce. Served with Coo coo aka CouCou. Creamy, thick and hearty Polenta made from cornmeal– Caribbean style. An intriguing side dish with tons of flavor. Served with Callaloo many consider this staple Trinidad's national dish. Earthy, Creamy, Jam Packed with Nutrients from Spinach, Coconut Milk, and traditional herbs and spices. GF. Available Filet Boneless or Whole Fish.

description: Cocobreeze Caribbean Restaurant & Bakery is an authentic Caribbean restaurant & vegan bakery in Maxwell Area, Oakland, CA. Customers can enjoy classic Caribbean food, from our oxtails, jerk chicken, doubles, curry goat roti, & Jamaican patties. We also offer vegan cuisine that's full of Jamaican flavor. Our superfood drinks are made w/healthy nutrient rich superfoods and adaptogens that help fortify your body & taste delicious. Our restaurant attracts locals from all over California's Bay Area, as well as out-of-town visitors.We also offer full service catering services so you can delight guests with our nutrient-rich Caribbean cuisine at your event. Taste the islands' authentic Caribbean cuisine at Cocobreeze Caribbean Restaurant & Bakery.
